how to build:
 
 git submodule init
 git submodule update
 cd externals && ruby build.rb && cd ..
 rm -rf build && mkdir build && cd build
 cmake ../src (cmake -G "Visual Studio 9 2008" .. on Windows)
 make (devenv LZMAService.sln on Windows)
 cd test && ruby ./runtests.rb && cd ..
 
A directory LZMA should be generated which is your service ready to 
be installed using the BrowserPlus SDK:
 
http://browserplus.yahoo.com/developer/service/sdk/
